## What is the Logitech MX Master 3S?
The **Logitech MX Master 3S** is widely considered the best productivity mouse available. It’s designed for power users — especially creators, coders, and anyone who spends long hours working with AI tools, editing content, or managing multiple screens.

## Why beginners love it
- Ultra-comfortable design for long sessions.
- **MagSpeed scroll wheel**: fly through hundreds of lines of text instantly.
- Customizable buttons for AI shortcuts (ex: launch ChatGPT, open Canva).
- Works on almost any surface, even glass.
- USB-C fast charging, lasts up to 70 days on one charge.

## Quick Start
1. Connect the mouse via Bluetooth or Logi Bolt USB receiver.  
2. Install Logitech Options+ software.  
3. Map side buttons to your favorite AI tools (like “Open ChatGPT” or “Paste Last Prompt”).  

## Why it’s perfect for AI users
When you’re constantly moving between browser tabs, AI dashboards, and content editing, small efficiency gains add up. With one button press, you can launch ChatGPT, copy-paste text, or open your content calendar — saving minutes every hour.

